movies.title: War Dogs
movies.plot: Based on the true story of two young men, David Packouz and Efraim Diveroli, who won a $300 million contract from the Pentagon to arm America's allies in Afghanistan.
movies.awards: Nominated for 1 Golden Globe. Another 2 nominations.

events.title: Efraim Diveroli finds "The Afghan deal" online
AEY win the Afghan deal contract
Efraim Diveroli is sentenced to four years in prison

movies.title: Captain America: Civil War
movies.plot: Following the events of Age of Ultron, the collective governments of the world pass an act designed to regulate all superhuman activity. This polarizes opinion amongst the Avengers, causing two factions to side with Iron Man or Captain America, which causes an epic battle between former allies.
